UID:9420c19f-d847-56f3-a4cb-14ed63396b19
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20240814T153000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20240814T173000
DESCRIPTION:Come meet your teacher\, see your friends and meet our new prin
 cipal\, Sra. Perez! We can't wait to see your smiling faces!\n\n\n\n\n\n 
SUMMARY:Open House
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260308T053939Z
UID:25cf2d8b-0950-5a30-bcd5-3f179d5b7fa9
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20240814T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20240814T180000
DESCRIPTION:We are thrilled to invite you to our annual Elementary School O
 pen House! This is a wonderful opportunity for students\, parents\, and th
 e community to explore our vibrant school and get a glimpse of the excitin
 g educational journey your child will embark on.\n\nEvent Highlights:\n\n\
 n	\n	Classroom Tours: Walk through our welcoming classrooms and see where 
 the learning magic happens. Meet our dedicated teachers and discover the i
 nnovative tools and resources that support a dynamic learning environment.
 \n	\n	\n	Meet the Teachers: Take this chance to chat with our passionate e
 ducators. They’ll share their teaching philosophy\, classroom expectatio
 ns\, and how they create an engaging and supportive atmosphere for every s
 tudent.\n	\n	\n	Curriculum Overview: Learn about our exciting curriculum a
 nd enrichment programs designed to foster curiosity\, critical thinking\, 
 and a love of learning.\n	\n	\n	Parent Resources: Discover the variety of 
 resources and support available to parents and guardians. From volunteer o
 pportunities to parent-teacher associations\, find out how you can get inv
 olved in our school community.\n	\n	\n	Refreshments: Enjoy light snacks an
 d beverages as you mingle with other families and staff members.\n	\n\n\nW
 e look forward to seeing you there and sharing the many wonderful things h
 appening at our school. Your presence will help us build a strong and supp
 ortive community for our students.\n\nLet’s make this a memorable evenin
 g filled with excitement and anticipation for the school year ahead!
LOCATION:Butte Elementary
SUMMARY:Open House
END:VEVENT
