DESCRIPTION:A field trip to Pyrah's Pioneer Peak Farm to learn about where 
 does our food come from\, what is the science behind plant lifecycles\, an
 d the history of the colonists in our area! SO much fun!!!!\n\nStudents mu
 st have a signed permission slip to attend. Bus will leave Sherrod at 9:30
  am and return at 12:15 pm. Don't miss out on this excellent experience!\
 n\n***The fee of $12.00 is a discounted fee for this trip\, representing
  Sherrod's status as a Community Eligibility Provision school this year
 .**** 
LOCATION:Pyrah's Pioneer Peak Farm
SUMMARY:Pyrah's Farm Experience for 3rd Grade
END:VEVENT
