UID:6f1d2b8c-6b98-55bc-abe7-8186ce477ee3
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20241210T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20241210T183000
DESCRIPTION:I plan for the concert to start at 6:00 P.M. and it should be o
 ver by 6:30 at the latest.\n\nFor my concerts I have all students singing 
 in the concert sitting with their grade at the front of the gym\, similarl
 y to how we had them for the Veterans day assembly.\n\nFor any teachers wh
 o are able to attend the concert\, all I would ask for you to help with wo
 uld be to sit by your grade to help monitor good audience behavior\, which
  I’ll be reviewing with the classes that will be performing\, and helpin
 g them to stand and find their way to the risers when it is their turn to 
 perform.\n\nIf you are able to attend\, and would like to see how the conc
 ert will go\, I will be doing a practice run through with each grade that 
 is performing on Tuesday December 5th during their specials.\n\nIf there i
 s time during the class day too\, I would appreciate it if the students mi
 ght be able to go over their songs\, the words and practice tracks I will 
 try to have on the Tanaina Music Website\n\nIf there are any other questio
 ns or concerns\, please let me know and I will do my best to address them!
 \n\n
LOCATION:
SUMMARY:Winter Concert K\, 4th\, Band
END:VEVENT
