DESCRIPTION:Click the link to register: https://forms.gle/JyBzem7eitvTHMCk
 7\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nTKE Community Schools Progr
 am SY24/25 \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nSusitna Valley Little Dribblers Ba
 sketball Camp (1st-3rd Grade) Registration\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nEven
 t Location:  TKE Gymnasium\n\nDays of the Week: Mondays and Wednesdays\n
 \nPractice Time: 3:05 - 4:30 pm\n\nPractice Begin Date: Monday\, January
  6\, 2025\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nPractice End Date: Wednesday\, Febru
 ary 12\, 2025\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nNO PRACTICE ON: Monday\, January
  20th and Monday\, February 10th\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n 
 \n\n \n\n \n\nCrowley Classic Tournament Date and Game Time: Saturday\,
  February 14\, 2025\, game time TBA \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nTournamen
 t Location: Susitna Valley Jr/Sr High School Gymnasium\n\n \n\n \n\n \
 n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nProgram Cost: $20 per athlete\n\n
  \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nEach registered athlete will take home one interme
 diate size basketball at the end of the season.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\
 n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nPersonalized jerseys will be available for 
 purchase for an additional $15.00. Jerseys will be available for purchase 
 on-site. \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nPaymen
 t details are pending. We will let you know as soon as possible how this w
 ill be handled. Thank you for your patience and understanding.\n\n \n\n 
 \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nA refund will be considered 
 for all circumstances. If a student is removed from Basketball Camp due to
  behavioral issues\, a refund will be issued.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n
  \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nAction Needed: \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n
 Complete the online registration form to sign up. \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n
  \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nThe Matanuska-Susitna Borough School D
 istrict Release of Liability Form must be completed by a parent or guardia
 n prior to athlete participation. A digital copy of the completed form may
  be emailed to Ms. Becks at rebecca.hrdy@matsuk12.us\, or a printed paper
  copy may be turned in by the first practice. Paper copies will also be av
 ailable in the front office.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nLittleDribblersRM1
 1StudentPermissionSliptoParticipate.pdf\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n
  \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nRegistration is due by the first day of practice.\
 n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nEnter your studen
 t's practices into https://parents.pikmykid.com//. \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\
 n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nDescription: \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n
  \n\nThis program fills quickly on a first-come\, first-served basis. Th
 e camp will be capped at 30 athletes. We will contact you if the camp is f
 ull.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nStudent Cond
 uct: Students are expected to be well-behaved at all times. This camp is 
 for athletes who are serious about having fun\, developing a love for bask
 etball\, and improving skills. If a child’s behavior creates any disrup
 tion for any reason\, the parent will be contacted to remove him/her immed
 iately and the child may not be allowed back into the camp in future years
 . You will be refunded your entry fee. \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\
 n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nEmergencies: If an emergency arises which will d
 elay you picking up your son or daughter on time\, please call or text the
  Coordinator of Basketball Camp Program\, Alysa Tunnell\, at (907) 355-
 3497. \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nFor the s
 afety of your child\, no student will be released to anyone except a paren
 t or guardian unless the student brings a signed and detailed note from 
 the parent or guardian telling us otherwise. If an emergency arises\, ple
 ase call us at the number listed above.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n
  \n\n 
LOCATION:TKE Gym
SUMMARY:CANCELLED TKE CS: Susitna Valley Little Dribblers Basketball Camp (
 1st-3rd Grade)
END:VEVENT
