DESCRIPTION:Click link to register: https://forms.gle/xhGmu3edDp12HeBH8\n\
 n \n\n \n\nEvent Location:  TKE Gymnasium\n\nDay of the Week: Mondays\
 n\nTime: 4:30 - 5:30 pm\n\nBegin Date: Monday\, October 7th\, 2024\n\n 
 \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nEnd Date: Monday\, May 12th\, 2025\n\n \n\n \n\n
  \n\n \n\nProgram Dates: Toddler Gym Time will be offered on an on-goin
 g\, regular\, drop-in basis throughout the school year\, excepting school 
 holidays\, closures\, etc. \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nNO TODDLER GYM ON:
  January 20th\, and March 10th\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nAction Required
 : Complete the registration to sign up. A separate\, paper-copy of the r
 elease of liability form will be provided and must be completed prior to p
 articipation.\n\n\n\nDescription:\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nThe Talkeetna
  Elementary gym and equipment will be open and available for children of t
 oddler age to come and play on a weekly basis throughout the school year\,
  free of charge. Toddler Gym Time is flexible\, lively\, fun\, and filled
  with heart-warming\, ear-piercing\, rafter-echoing toddler giggles!\n\n 
 \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nChildren above toddler age are welcome to attend\, w
 ith the understanding that activities and energy levels will be determined
  by the toddlers.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nPlease bring indoor shoes to 
 wear in the gym\; outdoor shoes and boots damage the gym floor. Barefeet o
 r socks are acceptable as well\, according to your comfort.\n\n \n\n \n\
 n \n\n \n\nAn adult responsible for the behavior\, safety\, and care of 
 the participating child or children must be present while the child is pre
 sent.\n\n \n\n 
LOCATION:TKE Gym
SUMMARY:CANCELLED TKE Community Schools: Toddler Gym Time
END:VEVENT
