UID:58d9d20f-ddb2-5672-9100-31241c7b8cc0
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20250116T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20250116T200000
DESCRIPTION:TKE Community Schools Program SY24/25 \n\nSky Watching: Our Dy
 namic Solar System presented by Kathleen Fleming\n\nClick link to register
 : https://forms.gle/u1LMd1EXHDsrQUQw9\n\nLearn about seasonal changes in 
 the night sky\, the wandering planets\, and the moon's movements.  Kathle
 en uses demonstrations\, visual aids and handouts to help participants und
 erstand why things appear as they do from here\, at 62 degrees north.\n\nW
 e will go outside for a brief orientation\, if the sky is clear.    \n\
 nSuitable for adults and interested youths 10 years or older.
LOCATION:TKE Library
SUMMARY:TKE CS: "Sky Watching: Our Dynamic Solar System" with Kathleen Flem
 ing
END:VEVENT
