DESCRIPTION:Click link to register: https://forms.gle/xhGmu3edDp12HeBH8\n\
 nEvent Location:  TKE Gymnasium\nDay of the Week: Mondays\nTime: 4:30 -
  5:30 pm\nBegin Date: Monday\, October 7th\, 2024\n\nEnd Date: Monday\, 
 May 12th\, 2025\n\nProgram Dates: Toddler Gym Time will be offered on an 
 on-going\, regular\, drop-in basis throughout the school year\, excepting 
 school holidays\, closures\, etc. \n\nNO TODDLER GYM ON: January 20th\, 
 and March 10th\n\nAction Required: Complete the registration to sign up.
  A separate\, paper-copy of the release of liability form will be provided
  and must be completed prior to participation.\n\nDescription:\n\nThe Talk
 eetna Elementary gym and equipment will be open and available for children
  of toddler age to come and play on a weekly basis throughout the school y
 ear\, free of charge. Toddler Gym Time is flexible\, lively\, fun\, and f
 illed with heart-warming\, ear-piercing\, rafter-echoing toddler giggles!\
 n\nChildren above toddler age are welcome to attend\, with the understandi
 ng that activities and energy levels will be determined by the toddlers.\n
 \nPlease bring indoor shoes to wear in the gym\; outdoor shoes and boots d
 amage the gym floor. Barefeet or socks are acceptable as well\, according 
 to your comfort.\n\nAn adult responsible for the behavior\, safety\, and c
 are of the participating child or children must be present while the child
  is present.
LOCATION:TKE Gym
SUMMARY:CANCELLED TKE Community Schools: Toddler Gym Time
END:VEVENT
