BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260308T053942Z
UID:ca25bdb2-4102-57ed-b551-921cef521781
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20250225T123000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20250225T143000
DESCRIPTION:Dear TKE Parent\,\n\nDuring the last week of February\,  we wi
 ll be showing the video\, "Puberty: A Girl's/Boy's Journey through the phy
 sical\, emotional\, and social changes"\, to 5th grade and "Meet the New Y
 ou for Girls/Boys!" for 4th grade..  These videos present the basic anato
 my and physiology that occurs as a child reaches puberty. An overview of t
 he videos can be found here:                           https
 ://marshmedia.com/collections/puberty-dvds \n\nLENGTH OF VIDEO: Between 1
 8-24 min with questions and discussions after.\n \nAs I watched the vide
 os\, I liked that they contained information to help your child understand
  his/her own body\, the way it works\, and the best ways to keep it health
 y. The website says: “This introduction is designed for your youngest st
 udents who are not quite ready to learn about reproduction\, but need to k
 now about body changes\, hygiene and emotional changes unique to girls. To
 pics include:\n\n-When to expect the onset of puberty\n-Physical and emoti
 onal changes\n-Menstruation\n-Importance of good hygiene\, exercise\, nutr
 ition and sleep\n-Self Esteem\n\nPlease also know there will be a Q&amp\;A
  and  I often give out information sheets and deodorant or sanitary napki
 n samples to students at the end of our session.  The students are direct
 ed to bring the information home and share it with parents and guardians.
   It is my hope that parents\, and guardians will be available to answer 
 any questions that their student may have after they have gone home for th
 e day.\n\nPlease sign and return the attached form to the front desk of Ta
 lkeetna Elementary.\n\nThank you\,\n\n\nRomy Byrd RN\n(907) 733-9400\nScho
 ol Nurse
SUMMARY:TKE Human Growth and Development\, 4th & 5th Grade
END:VEVENT
