DESCRIPTION:Dear Team\,Many of you have already heard that the district is 
 transitioning from Aimsweb to mClass (DIBELS) for early elementary benchma
 rk assessments. The state requires that all personnel involved in these as
 sessments complete training.DEED is offering one-day mClass training on Ma
 rch 26th and 27th. You only need to attend one of the two days. I will be 
 sending out the sign-up for both sessions—please register for the one th
 at best fits your schedule.📅 Date: Tuesday\, March 26th or Wednesday\, 
 March 27th⏰ Time: 8:45 AM – 3:45 PM📍 Location: New STEAM RoomIt mig
 ht be nice to coordinate bringing in some snacks for the day—more on tha
 t later! Let me know if you have any questions.Thanks\,Eric
LOCATION:
SUMMARY:mClass Training
END:VEVENT
