DESCRIPTION:Join us for a tour and tasting of Palmer's Kombucha brewery! Di
 scover the chemistry and health benefits behind a batch of Kombucha. Each 
 participant will enjoy a flight of kombucha drinks with unique flavors\, a
 nd a tour of the science and artistry behind each batch.People have consum
 ed kombucha\, a type of fermented tea\, for thousands of years. Not only d
 oes it have the same health benefits as tea — it’s also rich in benefi
 cial probiotics.Location: 203 Kombucha\, Palmer$5 per student. The cost of
  this activity will be automatically deducted from the student allotment.
LOCATION:
SUMMARY:Kombucha Tour and Tasting
END:VEVENT
