DESCRIPTION:Welcome Creatives!This year long course is developed to accommo
 date students who have demonstrated a strong interest and commitment to ex
 cel in visual arts. Students will develop a body of work that shows practi
 ce\, experimentation\, and revision to complete self-directed art themes p
 resented in an online portfolio. Research\, field trips\, group discussion
 \, written critiques\, and community display will be integral parts of thi
 s course.Jan 7 - May 13LOCATION: MCS ART ROOM
LOCATION:MCS Art Rm
SUMMARY:AP Art/Portfolio Development
