DESCRIPTION:My name is Carson Winell. I am a proud Mat-Su Central graduate\
 , a current Mat-Su Central substitute\, and proud to be a new Mat-Su Centr
 al instructional partner.I am very excited to open sign-ups for Semester 2
  Guitar Class. Here is some important info to remember about this class:  
 *   All guitar classes will be held in the music room at Mat-Su Central af
 ter MSC music classes. As a vendor\, my guitar classes are separate from M
 rs. Schwartz' music classes.  *   If your student does not have a guitar o
 f their own\, they can check one out from the Mat-Su Central music invento
 ry.  *   This class costs $200 per semester. I am a reimbursement vendor\,
  which means I will send you an invoice directly and provide you with an i
 nstructional receipt for you to get reimbursed.Timeframes:Beginning Guitar
  (3rd-5th) Wednesdays\, 2:15-2:45Beginning Guitar (6th-12th) Wednesdays\, 
 3:00-3:30Intermediate Guitar (All ages) Fridays\, 2:30-3:30
