DESCRIPTION:Intermediate Guitar (All ages) Fridays\, 2:30-3:30My name is Ca
 rson Winell. I am a proud Mat-Su Central graduate\, a current Mat-Su Centr
 al substitute\, and proud to be a new Mat-Su Central instructional partner
 .I am very excited to open sign-ups for Semester 2 Guitar Class. Here is s
 ome important info to remember about this class:  *   All guitar classes w
 ill be held in the music room at Mat-Su Central after MSC music classes. A
 s a vendor\, my guitar classes are separate from Mrs. Schwartz' music clas
 ses.  *   If your student does not have a guitar of their own\, they can c
 heck one out from the Mat-Su Central music inventory.  *   This class cost
 s $200 per semester. I am a reimbursement vendor\, which means I will send
  you an invoice directly and provide you with an instructional receipt for
  you to get reimbursed.
LOCATION:MCS Music Rm
SUMMARY:Intermediate Guitar (All ages) 
