DESCRIPTION: Mat-Su Borough School DistrictElementary School Chess Tourname
 ntSchedule and InformationDate:               Saturday\, April 5\, 2025Loc
 ation:        Colony Middle School Small GymFormat:          7 Round Swiss
  SystemFor fair and accurate scoring for all\, it is critical that players
  commit to playing all roundsTime Control: 7 rounds of “Game in 15” (G
 /15) - each player has 15’ for all their moves = 30’ max. roundsRoster
 s:         Player substitutions can be made at sign-in. No additional seat
 s can be added at tournament.See MSBSD Chess website for registration info
 rmation.Food:              At this time concessions are not assured\, plea
 se bring your own food. Coaches will be notified                        if
  concessions become available.Game Area:    All tournament games will take
  place in the CMS small gym. This area is to remain as quiet as possible. 
 As soon as players complete a round\, they will exit the tournament room a
 nd report to their team area (see below). Coaches and other adults wishing
  to observe the tournament games will have limited access to the tournamen
 t floor. Their will be a viewing area for quiet observation\, but communic
 ation with players during games is forbidden.Team Areas:  Team areas will 
 be in the CMS cafeteria.  There will be plenty of space for relaxing or co
 aching between games. Coaches should ensure that their team is supervised 
 when in the team area between games and during the lunch break. If teams b
 ring any chess equipment with them\, please be sure to have it clearly lab
 eled.Awards:         Individual 1st\, 2nd\, 3rd                        Tea
 m 1st\, 2nd\, 3rd (combined scores of top players/school)Schedule:       8
 :00 – 8:30                 Check-In8:30 – 8:50                  Q &amp
 \; A9:00 – 9:30                 Round 1 (G/15)9:30 – 9:40             
      Break9:40 – 10:10               Round 2 (G/15)10:10 – 10:20      
         Break10:20 – 10:50             Round 3 (G/15)10:50 - 11:00      
          Break11:00 - 11:30              Round 4 (G/15)11:30 – 12:10    
          Lunch Break12:10 – 12:40             Round 5 (G/15)12:40 – 12
 :50              Break12:50 – 1:20               Round 6 (G/15)1:20 – 
 1:30                  Break1:30 – 2:00                 Round 7 (G/15)2:0
 0 – 2:10                  Break2:10 – 2:20                 Award Cerem
 ony
LOCATION:Colony Middle School Small Gym
SUMMARY:Chess Tournament @ Colony Middle School Small Gym
END:VEVENT
