DESCRIPTION:Students will design layout\, then construct a balsa truss brid
 ge to be load tested (broken!). Who will design/construct the strongest br
 idge? We will discuss the 5 basic truss types before students make a choic
 e and start construction.Just a reminder\, this is only a request to enrol
 l. I will email you with confirmation.LOCATION: MCS ACTIVITY LAB – New B
 uilding*Schedule change: Class is now in the new building from 4/14-4/17.
LOCATION:MCS Activity Lab
SUMMARY:Breaking Bridges Workshop
