  needed—just bring your creativity and enthusiasm!  *   DATE: APRIL 16\,
  2025  *   TIME: 11:00 AM - 1:00 PM  *   LOCATION: MEET US AT 3 RIVERS FLY
  AND TACKLE\, 390 Railroad Ave Wasilla  *   COST: $100 includes personaliz
 ed instruction and all materials. The cost for this activity will be autom
 atically deducted from the student’s allotmentSIGN-UP: https://forms.gle
 /jpBZwmsQ67iDQzJR9
