DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20250501T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20250501T140000
DESCRIPTION:Congratulations on accomplishing your i-Ready goals!  For stude
 nts who have passed 24 math and/or reading lessons since December 6th\, yo
 u’re invited to a party at North Bowl.  This activity includes bowling\,
  pizza\, and soda.  Hooray!\n\n  *   Date: May 1\, 2025\n  *   Time: 12:00
  - 2:00 PM\n  *   Location: Meet us at North Bowl\, 3250 E Palmer-Wasilla 
 Hwy\, Wasilla\n  *   Cost: MCS will cover the cost for all qualified I-Rea
 dy students.\n  *   NOTE Regarding Additional Participants: Siblings enrol
 led with MCS are welcome to attend and can use their allotment to pay for 
 the bowling activity ($12.50 Per Person). Siblings not enrolled with MCS a
 nd or adults wishing to bowl can pay for their game via School Pay ($12.50
  Per Person). A payment link will be sent directly to your email.\n  *   M
 CS Permission Slip\n  *   REQUIRED: WEAR SOCKS\n\n\n
LOCATION:
SUMMARY:i-Ready Bowling Party
END:VEVENT
