BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260308T053943Z
UID:938b379f-efac-56ed-8a11-eb634d39f2e5
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20250506T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20250506T160000
DESCRIPTION:Good afternoon\,\n\n\n\nInformation was sent out at the end of 
 March regarding the transition from American Fidelity to Voya Financial an
 d we have been diligently working through the implementation. We are excit
 ed to have a draft schedule for onsite enrollment with representatives for
  benefits through Voya for your review. Below is a link to the schedule. 2
 1 sites will be visited in-person this year from May 5th – May 16th. We 
 have worked to provide options close by for employees that may need to tra
 vel to another school for an appointment. Once all appointments the first 
 week have been booked\, the appointments the second week will be available
  for employees to select.\n\n\n\nVoya will also be providing call center a
 ppointments for employees to ask questions and receive help with enrolling
  from May 5th – May 17th. There will be evening and weekend appointments
  available in addition to times throughout the workday. Also\, an online s
 elf-enrollment option will be available through May 31st. We will be sendi
 ng out detailed information to employees next week about open enrollment a
 nd we ask that you please not share the onsite schedule with employees\, a
 s it is not finalized.\n\n\n\nIf your school is listed on the schedule at 
 the link below\, please enter additional information in the boxes on the r
 ight by the end of the day on Monday\, April 28th. We appreciate your help
 ! We will do our best to take into consideration any requested schedule pr
 eferences. If your school is not listed on the schedule and you have any c
 oncerns\, please feel free to contact me.\n\n\n\nhttps://docs.google.com/s
 preadsheets/d/1VyVOI3oSHinY38F5gL7xzBTywgKVgnWI/edit?usp=sharing&amp\;ouid
 =102618214246897466539&amp\;rtpof=true&amp\;sd=true\n\n\n\nThank you\,\n\n
 Sunshine\n\n\n\nSunshine Hunsaker – Director of Finance\n\nMatanuska-Sus
 itna Borough School District\n\nPh: 907-746-9260 | Fax: 907-761-4091\n\nww
 w.matsuk12.us\n\n\n\n
LOCATION:staff lounge
SUMMARY:VOYA (formerly America Fidelity) in the Staff Lounge All Day
END:VEVENT
