DESCRIPTION:Take a hike... with MCS Club 100!Let’s hit the trail for some
  fresh air\, exercise &amp\; sunshine. Bring your friends or make some new
  ones &amp\; explore the trails with Mat-Su Central School. This is a 3 mi
 le\, moderate to difficult hike up the Butte.Location: Meet us at the trai
 lhead: Take the Old Glenn Hwy. from Palmer\, turn right at the first "Bode
 nburg Loop". Turn left on Mothershead Dr. After about 1/4 of a mile you wi
 ll see the parking area on the left. This is a borough maintained trail an
 d parking lot. There is a fee to park.
LOCATION:
SUMMARY:Take a hike... with MCS Club 100!
END:VEVENT
