 ricts\, state agencies\, trade and professional organizations collaborate 
 to provide the students with an introduction to various aspects of constru
 ction.\n\nSpecial notes: 8:00 AM arrival is critical because MCS students 
 will move through the stations as a group.  At the check-in desk meet MCS 
 advisor\, Joe Rucker.\n*Students must complete and return their registrati
 on and waiver forms to kristin.langhoff@matsuk12.us before attending.\n\n
