DESCRIPTION:Meet the Musk Ox babies!Join MSCS on a fun and furry trip to th
 e Musk Ox Farm in Palmer!We will tour the farm\, meet the babies\, learn a
 bout their diet\, habitat\, and behaviors.Cost: Both the student and (one)
  parent admission cost will be automatically deducted from the student all
 otment. $6 per student $10 per adult. Siblings 2 and under are free.Note: 
 Additional parents and children are welcome to attend and pay for entrance
