BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260308T053943Z
UID:b1d15b77-7784-5473-aa23-be20e966849a
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20250514T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20250514T140000
DESCRIPTION:Hey Mat-Su Central Class of 2025! 🎓\nYou did it! After all t
 he hard work\, late nights\, and unforgettable memories\, it’s time to c
 elebrate you! Join us for one final epic hurrah at the 2025 Senior Fun Day
 !\n\n  *   Date: May 14\, 2025\n  *   Time: 11:00 AM - 2:00 PM\n  *   Nort
 h Bowl\n  *\nThis event costs $15 per person for all MCS 2025 graduates. G
 uests are $15 Per person.  The fee for you and your guest (if applicable) 
 can be automatically deducted from your student allotment. If your allotme
 nt doesn’t have enough funds\, you can pay through School Pay. A payment
  link will be emailed to you.\nSTRIKE up some fun\, laughter\, and lasting
  memories with your fellow graduates!  Don’t miss out—this event is al
 l about celebrating YOU. See you there!\n\nGuests: MCS seniors can invite 
 ONE guest\, The guest must be either a graduating senior or a junior in go
 od standing. If you choose to invite one guest\, you must include his/ her
  full name &amp\; name of the school he / she attends. If you bring a gues
 t\, he/ she can play all the games and partake in the food and beverages a
 t the party but will not be eligible to participate in the prize drawings.
 \nThe RSVP deadline is May 9\nGraduation Checklist\nMCS Permission Slip\n\
 n\n
LOCATION:
SUMMARY:2025 Senior Day! 
END:VEVENT
