UID:8c0b9bb2-a274-5c51-a71f-e626b6d1262b
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20250521T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20250521T090000
DESCRIPTION:Dear Talkeetna Elementary Families\,\n\nAs you are aware\, our 
 school has experienced eight snow days this year\, and we must adjust our 
 calendar to ensure that our students receive the required instructional ti
 me needed to support their learning. The following dates will now be regul
 ar school days when students are expected to attend:\n\n\n	February 10 (
 Previously a Parent-Teacher Conference day)\n	February 17 (Previously a P
 arent-Teacher Conference day)\n	March 7 (Previously a Teacher Work Day)\n
 	May 2 (Previously a Professional Learning Day)\n	May 21 (Previously a S
 cheduled Snow Day)\n	May 23 (Previously a Teacher Work Day)\n\n\nPlease n
 ote that this adjustment includes one additional student contact day at th
 e end of the school year.\n\nWe understand that these changes may present 
 challenges for some families\, and we sincerely appreciate your patience a
 nd flexibility as we navigate this unusual school year. Our goal is to ens
 ure that our students continue to receive the education they deserve while
  meeting the required instructional hours.\n\nIn addition to these changes
 \, we recognize the importance of Parent-Teacher Conferences. To make up f
 or the loss of our previously scheduled conferences\, teachers will be con
 tacting families to arrange phone conferences. We will prioritize Reads Ac
 t conversations for Tier 2 and Tier 3 students. Please look for an informa
 tional letter in your students homework folder next week. \n\nThank you f
 or your understanding and support as we work together to make the best of 
 these adjustments. If you have any questions or concerns\, please do not h
 esitate to reach out to the school office.\n\nSincerely\,\nDrew Larrabee\n
 Principal\, Talkeetna Elementary School
LOCATION:Talkeetna Elementary School\, E Timberwolf Loop\, Talkeetna\, AK\,
  USA
SUMMARY:TKE School Day: Snow Day Make-Up
END:VEVENT
