DESCRIPTION:MCS Musicians and families\,\nYou are invited to a fun activity
  at the Fly Trampoline Park! Let's celebrate a fantastic year of musical g
 rowth and camaraderie at Wasilla’s trampoline adventure complex filled w
 ith interconnected padded trampolines and much more! Attractions include\,
  interconnected trampolines\, games\, foam zone\, ninja course\, warped wa
 ll\, and arcade.\n\n  *   Date: Thursday\, May 22\, 2025\n  *   Time: Chec
 k-in at 1:15\, jump time runs 1:30 - 2:30 PM\, Arcade time runs 2:30 - 3:0
 0 PM.\n  *   Cost: $16\; includes 1 hour jump time\, jump socks\, and a $1
 0 arcade card (must be used directly after jump time. No redemption tix). 
 The cost of this activity will be automatically deducted from the students
  allotment. Trampoline Park passes may not be used as payment.\n  *   Loca
 tion: Meet us at the Fly Trampoline Park\, 1841 Parks Hwy. (By Target).\n 
  *   All student participants must be enrolled in MSC\; we cannot accommod
 ate younger siblings under 4 yrs. old.\n  *   Required: All participants m
 ust sign a Fly Trampoline Waiver at: https://flytrampolinepark.com/wasilla
 /waiver/ \n  *   MCS Student Permission Slip\n\n\n
LOCATION:
SUMMARY:MUSIC STUDENTS FLY AT THE TRAMPOLINE PARK!
END:VEVENT
