UID:e8890eec-8c3f-5a8f-aa44-ed74d7d4989e
DTSTART;TZID=America/Juneau:20250603T163000
DTEND;TZID=America/Juneau:20250603T180000
DESCRIPTION:Click link to register: https://forms.gle/xhGmu3edDp12HeBH8Eve
 nt Location:  TKE Gymnasium\nDay of the Week: Mondays\nTime: 4:30 - 5:3
 0 pm\nBegin Date: Monday\, October 7th\, 2024End Date: Monday\, May 12th
 \, 2025Program Dates: Toddler Gym Time will be offered on an on-going\, r
 egular\, drop-in basis throughout the school year\, excepting school holid
 ays\, closures\, etc. NO TODDLER GYM ON: January 20th\, and March 10thAc
 tion Required: Complete the registration to sign up. A separate\, paper-
 copy of the release of liability form will be provided and must be complet
 ed prior to participation.\n\nDescription:The Talkeetna Elementary gym and
  equipment will be open and available for children of toddler age to come 
 and play on a weekly basis throughout the school year\, free of charge. T
 oddler Gym Time is flexible\, lively\, fun\, and filled with heart-warming
 \, ear-piercing\, rafter-echoing toddler giggles!Children above toddler ag
 e are welcome to attend\, with the understanding that activities and energ
 y levels will be determined by the toddlers.Please bring indoor shoes to w
 ear in the gym\; outdoor shoes and boots damage the gym floor. Barefeet or
  socks are acceptable as well\, according to your comfort.An adult respons
 ible for the behavior\, safety\, and care of the participating child or ch
 ildren must be present while the child is present.
LOCATION:TKE Gym
SUMMARY:TKE CS: Toddler Gym Time
END:VEVENT
