 ng your laptops and your questions. After the meeting Stacey will also be 
 available for hands-on help as needed.Also — let’s make it a little mo
 re fun: bring a favorite brunch dish to share. Coffee will be flowing\, so
  come hungry and ready to catch up.Looking forward to seeing everyone!–E
 ric
