DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20251028
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20251029
DESCRIPTION:Hello\, I wanted to let you guys know about Red Ribbon week!We 
 will be participating the 28-30st   3 days next week.Before school on Tues
 day\, I will set up the table on the multi-purpose stage.Please visit the 
 table with your class at some point on these three days.  *   On the table
  you will find small paper ribbons. These are for each student to write th
 eir name on and tape to the banner for pledging to be drug free.  *   Then
  each student may get One of the following: bracelet OR temporary tattoo O
 R Sticker. I have enough for one for each student. First come first serve.
   *   Please talk with your team about what lesson is to be shared with yo
 ur students.Please reach out if you have any questions.Amy Murrell RN\, BS
 N\, NCSNSchool Nurse at Machetanz Elementary907-864-2304
LOCATION:
SUMMARY:Red Ribbon Week Oct. 28-30
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
